{
  "stem": "11882.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "At any rate, getting there was funny.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Mama Giese, of course, like Germans do-- I don't know whether you know about that-- in the afternoon, especially on Sunday, they have coffee and kuchen.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I was sometimes trusted-- I went to church at that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I was rather an earnest person and wanted to pray for my relatives while I was so far away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And on the way home from church, I went to the wonderful German cake store and picked out the cake for the afternoon coffee cake, and took it home to Mama Giese and Ingeborg.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they invited some friends, and then we'd have a coffee on Sunday afternoon.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And on the way, I was quite puzzled, but it happened to me several times.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People would step up to me and say, do you know-- in Deutsche, but I could see what they wanted-- do you know where such and such a street is?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I thought, do they think I-- do they think I know where these streets are?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I thought, well, I suppose I look like a German, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was-- [LAUGHS] I felt so strange, as an American girl, just dropped into this area.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was quite puzzled that they often would come up and-- not in a mean way-- would say, we can't find such a street, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It occurred to me, gradually, that Germans didn't look any different from anyone else.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And [LAUGHS] anyway, one got educated as one moved around, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it was a little interesting experience, because I went through all this without any knowledge of German to speak of, hardly.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know-- and many times, strange.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hmm?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Hitler came to town, and we had a day off.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
